# 9. 何度でも

Tsukasa: Are you ready with your side of the net, Rion?
Rion: Y-Yes!
Emu: I'm also ready!
Tsukasa: Alright, here we go. Take aim at Emu... One, two...!
Rion: Three!
Emu: Oh no! You caught me!
Tsukasa: Okay, we've got our timing down, so that should be enough for practice. Thank you for your assistance, Emu!
Tsukasa: Now, our next step is to—
Phoenix: You appear to be dragging your feet somewhat. Do you have any intention of actually catching me?
Tsukasa: Yes, we're ready to now! We will catch you, so prepare yourself!
Tsukasa: Let's go, Rion, Robo-Nene!
Rion: O-Okay...!
Robo-Nene: Battery reserves sufficient. All servos functioning normally.
Robo-Nene: Ready to super-jump at any time.
Tsukasa: Then, we'll launch once it's right above us!
Robo-Nene: Roger.
Tsukasa: Alright, now!
Emu: Wow! They're really flying!!!
Miku: Cool! So far so good☆
KAITO: I have a feeling that they'll reach the phoenix.
Phoenix: What...?
Tsukasa: Now, Rion! Cast the net!
Rion: Okay! C-Casting...!
Phoenix: ...!
Rion: Oh no...! Th-The wind...!
Tsukasa: (No, we missed... That means...!)
Tsukasa: It won't even reach it...!
Robo-Nene: Preparing to land. Brace for impact.
Tsukasa: Phew... Good work, Rui. That landing wasn't bad at all.
Tsukasa: However...
KAITO: Are you two okay?
Rion: Yes, we are! But more importantly...
Phoenix: That was somewhat alarming, but ultimately a childish attempt.
Tsukasa: Grr...
Rion: I'm so sorry... If only I'd cast my end of the net a little better...
Tsukasa: Don't worry about that! We still have a couple more attempts left, so let's just try again!
Tsukasa: Are you ready, Robo-Nene?
Robo-Nene: Yes. Ready to super-jump at any time.
Tsukasa: Alright, we'll get it this time...!
Phoenix: Oh, you're back.
Rion: N-Now...! Huh...?!
Tsukasa: (No... Now we've cast it too early...!)
Rion: I-I'm sorry for rushing...! I was so sure that we'd catch it, so I got ahead of myself and...
Tsukasa: That's okay! The phoenix hasn't gone anywhere, so let's just give it another try.
Rion: But Robo-Nene only has enough charge left for one more jump, right...?
Tsukasa: ...! Yes, we only had three attempts...
Rion: I'm so sorry... This is all my fault...
Rion: I guess I just don't have what it takes to catch that phoenix...
Tsukasa: Rion...
Tsukasa: I understand what you're going through.
Tsukasa: No matter how hard you try, you can never seem to reach your goal... I know that feeling all too well.
KAITO: Tsukasa...
Tsukasa: But are you okay with just giving up?
Rion: What...?
Tsukasa: Are you willing to give up on your dream after making just a couple of attempts at it?
Tsukasa: I don't think you should!
Rion: ...!
Tsukasa: Your eyes glistened as you spoke about that phoenix. You even had all those notes and records on it at your house...
Tsukasa: Which means you should not give up on your dream. Not so quickly!
Rion: Tsukasa...
Rion: But my hands... They won't stop shaking...
Rion: A part of me doesn't think I can do this. I'm struggling to find the confidence...
Rion: And you're going out of your way to help me... That just makes me feel even worse...
Tsukasa: No, that's a good thing.
Tsukasa: Keep that feeling in mind because it will help you succeed.
Rion: Huh...?
Tsukasa: What I'm trying to say is...
Tsukasa: The frustration and despair you're feeling will drive you to succeed. They'll help you move forward!
Rion: They will?
Tsukasa: Yes! Trust me, Rion. I guarantee that those feelings will help you succeed.
Tsukasa: Don't run from them. Accept your current situation and keep pushing forward...
Tsukasa: If you do so, your dream will come true!!
Rion: Oh...
Rion: O-Okay...!
KAITO: (You're right, Tsukasa.)
KAITO: (Because that's exactly what you've been doing.)
KAITO: (All in order to become a star who can make the whole world smile...)
KAITO: (It's a colossal dream, but that hasn't stopped you... You've faced a myriad of challenges and obstacles along the way, so I'm sure you'll...)
KAITO: Tsukasa, Rion... No matter what happens, we'll be there for you both. So, please do your best.
Emu: Plus, if this doesn't work out, we can always come up with a different way to make your dream come true!
Rion: Th-Thank you very much, KAITO, Emu!
Tsukasa: But for now, this is our last attempt...
Tsukasa: Let's go!
Tsukasa: (Phoenix...!)
Tsukasa: (We will catch you... It doesn't matter how high you fly. We will succeed!)
Tsukasa: Now, Rion! Cast the net!
Rion: O-Okay!
Phoenix: ...!
Tsukasa: (No, it dodged the net...!)
Rion: Oh no...!
Tsukasa: (We couldn't reach it...! No, we still have a chance...)
Tsukasa: Don't give up, Rion! Keep trying!
Tsukasa: No matter how hard it may seem, keep trying to make your dream come true!
Rion: Right...!
Phoenix: Huh...?! What are they...?
Tsukasa: *Roar*
Rion: *Scream*
Tsukasa: We can make iiiiiit!!!
Nene: They're flying...
Emu: Hey, look...! Tsukasa's hand touched the phoenix!
KAITO: Everyone! Get the landing pad ready!
Tsukasa: Noooooooooo! We're falling!!!!!
Rion: Waaaaahhhhh!
Miku: Tsukasa! Rion! Are you two okay...?
Tsukasa: Y-Yes... Thank goodness for the landing pad...
Rion: I-I'm also fine... Thank you very much.
Robo-Nene: Low battery reserves. Entering power-saving mode.
Nene: Thanks for all your hard work, Robo-Nene.
Tsukasa: Wait, the phoenix!
Tsukasa: We failed again...
Rion: I-I'm so sorry, everyone... Even after all the help you've given me...
Emu: No, don't apologize! Wait, huh?
Emu: Tsukasa, look! There's something stuck to your back!
Tsukasa: Hm? What's this...?
KAITO: It's a phoenix feather.
Tsukasa: A phoenix feather...?
KAITO: It looks like you reached it, if only briefly.
Tsukasa: Yes, it seems that way!
Phoenix: To think that you could lay a hand on me...
Rion: Ph-Phoenix...?!
Phoenix: I am still struggling to understand how creatures without wings such as yourselves could reach me.
Tsukasa: But...
Phoenix: Yes, you merely touched me. You did not catch me as we agreed.
Tsukasa: Grr...
Phoenix: But you do not plan on giving up, yes?
Rion: Huh...?
Phoenix: The day you do finally manage to catch me, I shall grant your wish.
Tsukasa: R-Really?!
Phoenix: Yes. That day may never actually come, but I can use this as a way to pass the time.
Rion: *Gasp* Th-Thank you very much...!
Phoenix: Also, I believe you were looking for this...
Emu: Oh, the map we found on that ship!
Tsukasa: What?! I'd completely forgotten about that!
Nene: Wait, you seriously forgot?
Rui: Hehe. That's very like you, Tsukasa. I was actually under the impression that you were refraining from bringing that up so as not to steal the spotlight from Rion.
Tsukasa: I-In any case, we need that...! So, Phoenix, please return it to us!
Phoenix: Yes, fine.
Nene: Huh? Really...?
Phoenix: Did I not say that I would do as you say if you managed to catch me?
Phoenix: So, think of this as a small reward for even touching me.
Emu: Wow! Thanks, Phoenix!
Tsukasa: Yes, thank you very much!
Phoenix: Your name is Rion, yes? Please come back to try and catch me whenever you like.
Rion: *Gasp*
Rion: Y-Yes, I will...!
Len: Oh, there it goes...
Emu: But it sorta gave us a smile before it left...!
KAITO: What if this is that phoenix's way of expressing its happiness over having finally found a worthy adversary?
Miku: Maybe☆ That means you gotta catch it someday!
Rion: Yes, you're right!
Rion: Thank you for what you did, Tsukasa.
Rion: I'm going to accept my shortcomings and keep moving forward. I'm going to make my dream come true someday...
Rion: I agree with what you said, Tsukasa. And I was able to take a big step today as a result.
Tsukasa: Rion...
Rion: I promise to keep doing my best. I'm going to keep chasing after that phoenix, and catch it someday.
Rion: And I will get it to let me fly on its back!
Tsukasa: Yes, keep trying!
Rion: I will!
Tsukasa: (Yes...)
Tsukasa: (No matter how hard things get, no matter how much you fail, you have to keep trying.)
Tsukasa: (That's how I'm going to make my dream come true.)
KAITO: Nice work, Tsukasa.
KAITO: I was impressed by how you were able to inspire Rion to keep chasing after his dream.
Tsukasa: Hm? You were? I was just doing what I always do! Hah hah hah hah hah!
Tsukasa: But I also felt inspired.
Tsukasa: Seeing Rion want to keep chasing after his dream made me want to do the same.
KAITO: Tsukasa...
KAITO: Yes, I also feel the same way.
Tsukasa: Hm? You do?
KAITO: Yes, because you'll all likely be faced with all sorts of challenges as you keep moving ahead.
KAITO: However, as you helped Rion just now...
KAITO: I plan on giving you all the support I can. Watching you today reaffirmed that for me.
Tsukasa: ...!
Tsukasa: Thank you, KAITO! I promise to not let those words go to waste. Because I am...
Tsukasa: Destined to become a star who makes the whole world smile!
